Install Java Jdk:

$ java -version
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install default-jdk

Install Scala:

$ scala –version
$ sudo apt-get install scala

#code
object Sample {
         def main(args: Array[String]) = {
                 println(“Hello, world”)
         }
}


Compile the Code In terminal:

scalac [Yourfilename].scala

#Ex. scalac sample.scala

Run the Scala Program:

scala [ObjectName]

#Ex.  scala Sample

